text: Gaede may refer to: * Bill Gaede (born 1952), Argentine engineer, programmer and Cold War industrial spy * Enrico Gaede (born 1982), German footballer * Heinrich Moritz Gaede (1795−1834), German naturalist and entomologist * Kevin Gaede (born 1959), known as Kevin Gage, American actor * Max Gaede (1871–1946), German entomologist and engineer * Wolfgang Gaede (1878–1945), German physicist and pioneer of vacuum engineering Gaede may also refer to * 14224 Gaede, main-belt asteroid
